				\begin{document}$$\chi _{ss - {\mathrm{CH}}_3}^{\left( 2 \right)}/\chi _{ss - {\mathrm{CH}}_2}^{\left( 2 \right)}$$\end{document} ratio, we fit the SFG spectra using a standard procedure (Supplementary Note 6). The χss−CH32/χss−CH22\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
